name: CryptoSerpent #007
description: Casper Rambowl enjoys going watching action movies, vandalising bus stops and drone photography. He is entertaining, but can also be very unfriendly and a bit sadistic.   He is obsessed with cigarettes. A year ago he saved a Cryptoserpent from a CryptoTrap for Cryptobears and to this day he continues to exaggerate it to the children of the park because he dreams of being a hero.
